i have oranges.

every day, i make a decision.
on how many oranges i'd eat.

i could eat a single orange.
or eat a couple.

well, sort of.
if the oranges can be split in equal halves.
i can eat an entire half.

if the oranges can be split in three equal parts.
then i can eat two parts.

so, i kinda have three decisions i can make.
two of them are conditional.

i can eat a single orange, no conditions.

or eat half of them, if the oranges can be split in equal halves.
or eat two thirds of them, if the oranges can be split three equal ways.

if i can only take one of these decisions per day.
how fast can finish all the oranges?

how many days?

NOW, TO SOLVE.

try every way, see what's quickest.